data.title: DVS "iPandemonium!" FULL TOUR VIDEO
data.description:
Originally appeared
In conjunction with Thrasher Magazine, the DVS squad invades Costa Rica, Panama, and Peru, slaying demos while still handling lots of business in the streets. Torey caps things off with that massive nollie flip from Thrasher's March cover. Boom!

data.title: Torey Pudwill Introduces The Torey 3 by DVS
data.description:
DVS is proud to unveil the Torey 3 Mid featuring VAPORCELL Lightweight Cushioning Technology. Torey Pudwill's latest signature shoe is the ultimate cupsole skate shoe designed to be lightweight, durable, and comfortable. 


Filmed & edited by Erik Bragg
Produced by DVS Shoe Company
